name: EMPEROR 20s.
description: where the 20s is a very productive age, where people also often remind us not to waste this age, every young person all works hard, is passionate, persistent to achieve his goals, forms a foundation, and has a burning passion, they provide themselves with the character of a father who works hard on their shoulders and the character of a mother who is always kind and unselfish in heart and firmness of womanhood, who in the future they can become emperors of the peak of their respective achievements.
